<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Reset Password</title>
  <style>
    /* Add your custom styles here */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .reset-code {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 8px 15px;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      color: #333;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
    <p>Hello {{ name }},</p>
    <p>We have received a request to reset your password for your account. If you didn't request this, you can ignore this email.</p>
    <p>To reset your password, use the following 6-character reset code:</p>
    <p class="reset-code">{{ code }}</p>
    <p>This reset code will expire after 10 minutes, so make sure to use it promptly.</p>
    <p>If you have not requested a password reset, no further action is required.</p>
    <p>Thank you,</p>
    <p>The Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
